其误差的不可避免性：无法用<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2398-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;X&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-18926" role="math" style="width: 0.917em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.714em; height: 0px; font-size: 123%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.73em, 1000.714em, 2.696em, -999.997em); top: -2.538em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-18927"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-18928" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">X<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.053em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.543em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.059em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 0.941em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>X</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2398">X</script>中含有的信息来解释<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2399-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;&amp;#x03B5;&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-18929" role="math" style="width: 0.561em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.46em; height: 0px; font-size: 123%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.933em, 1000.46em, 2.696em, -999.997em); top: -2.538em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-18930"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-18931" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">ε</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.543em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.059em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 0.691em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>ε</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2399">\varepsilon</script>，即使<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2400-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;Y&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-18932" role="math" style="width: 0.917em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.714em; height: 0px; font-size: 123%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.73em, 1000.714em, 2.696em, -999.997em); top: -2.538em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-18933"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-18934" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">Y<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.104em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.543em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.059em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 0.941em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>Y</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2400">Y</script>的估计<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inh