lar; position: absolute; top: -4.012em; left: 4.372em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-19040" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular; padding-left: 0.206em;">+</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-19041" style="padding-left: 0.206em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19042"><span class="munderover" id="MathJax-Span-19043"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.255em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.204em, 1002.645em, 4.322em, -999.997em); top: -4.012em; left: 0.257em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19044"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19045" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">V<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.104em;"></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19046" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19047" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">r<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.003em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-19048" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19049" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">ε</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-19050" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">)</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.001em, 1003.255em, 3.61em, -999.997em); top: -2.792em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-19051" style=""><span style="font-family: STIXSizeFiveSym;">⏟</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.543em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -1.434em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 2.691em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>Y</mi><mo>−</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>Y</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi>ε</mi><mo>−</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-OP MJX-fixedlimits"><munder><mrow><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>X</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><msup><mo stretchy="false">]</mo><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mo>⏟</mo></munder></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-OP MJX-fixedlimits"><munder><mrow><mi>V</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>ε</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mo>⏟</mo></munder></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2409">E(Y-\hat{Y})^{2} = E[f(X) + \varepsilon - \hat{f}(x)]^2=\underbrace{[f(X) - \hat{f}(X)]^2} + \underbrace{Var(\varepsilon)}</script></p>

<p>前半部分是可约误差——可以通过不断寻找更接近真实<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2410-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mi&gt;f&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;/math&gt;" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-19052" role="math" style="width: 0.561em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.46em; height: 0px; font-size: 123%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.73em, 1000.46em, 2.899em, -999.997em); top: -2.538em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19053"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19054" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.155em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.543em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.309em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 1.191em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>f</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2410">f</script>的<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2411-Frame" tabindex="0" data-mathml="&lt;math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;&gt;&lt;mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;&gt;&lt;mover&gt;&lt;mi&gt;f&lt;/mi&gt;&lt;mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;&gt;&amp;#x005E;&lt;/mo&gt;&lt;/mover&gt;&lt;/mrow&gt;&lt;/math&gt;" role="presentation" style="position: relative;"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-19055" role="math" style="width: 0.714em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.561em; height: 0px; font-size: 123%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.07em, 1000.511em, 2.543em, -999.997em); top: -2.182em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19056"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-19057"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-19058"><span class="munderover" id="MathJax-Span-19059"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.511em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.204em, 1000.409em, 4.372em, -999.997em); top: -4.012em; left: 0.003em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-19060" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.155em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.317em; left: 0.155em;"><span style="height: 0.003em; vertical-align: 0.003em; width: 0.409em; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden;"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-19061" style="font-family: STIXGeneral-Regular;">̂&nbsp;<span style="height: 0.003em; vertical-align: 0.003em; margin-left: -0.658em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.003em;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.017em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.309em; border-left-width: 0px; border-left-style: solid; width: 0px; height: 1.566em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mover><mi>f</mi><mo stretchy="false">^</mo></mover></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2411">\hat f</script>来减少，后半部分是不可约误差——那就好好忽略它吧; )</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>不可约误差提供了预测精度的一个上界，这个上界在实践中是未知的。</p>
</blockquote>

<p>上述角度来源于「预测」——关注误差重于一切，实际上是更偏向于工程的角度，这块的发展也由实际需求在不断推动。还有一种角度更关心的则是「推断」——X与Y之间的关系到底是怎样的？Y如何被X以怎样的程度影响...</p>

<p>预测还是推断，这个对于模型的构建非常重要。例如，若为了推断，往往采用的是参数模型，最简单的就是线性模型，变量之间的相互影响一目了然。</p>
<!-- content end -->
